<section>
    <title>Benefits of MDMI 2.0</title>       
        <itemizedlist mark='bullet' spacing='compact'>
            <listitem>
              <para>
                Precision
              </para>
            
			        <itemizedlist mark='bullet' spacing='compact'>
			           <listitem>
			              <para>
				            Insurance that each business element is unique. The requirement is to have disjointed semantic concepts/classes in the SEER linked to Concepts in SOLOR.
			             </para> 
			           </listitem>
			        </itemizedlist>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para>
			               Search
                </para>
			         <itemizedlist mark='bullet' spacing='compact'>
			               <listitem>
			                   <para>
				                    An improved search mechanism for the over 3,500 business elements in SEER (the number is continuously growing)
			                   </para>
			               </listitem>
			               <itemizedlist mark='bullet' spacing='compact'>
				                    <listitem>
				                          <para>
				                              New capability: a classification system based on disjoint classes where users can employ standard “programming” techniques
				                          </para>
				                  </listitem>
			               </itemizedlist>
                   </itemizedlist>
                 </listitem>
			   <listitem>
			         <para>
				          The use of semantic web technologies for discovery.
				      </para>
			   </listitem>
      </itemizedlist>
